: The 
<typeStatus id="54FC8811FFF83B7FFACCFA1E726D9DBE" box="[1295,1341,1472,1496]" pageId="24" pageNumber="57">type</typeStatus>
locality is situated in 
<collectingRegion id="4983F851FFF83B7FFC16FA3E73DF9D9E" box="[981,1167,1504,1528]" country="Malaysia" name="Pahang" pageId="24" pageNumber="57">Pahang Province</collectingRegion>
